{"tid":1943494,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"HKBN tracert有奇怪嘢","createTime":"2020-03-25T17:24:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T07:00:32.000Z","uid":86383,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e25191c55b2073c763a406eb2e9460fcdb270dd9","tid":1943494,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T17:24:34.000Z","msg":"HKBN 100MB家居用戶<br />\n2020年3月25日晚上9:30後<br />\n遊玩台灣online game時發生嚴重連線不穩定情況。<br />\n在同一隻game亦有其他同樣使用HKBN服務嘅玩家表示有相同情況。<br />\n<br />\n2020年3月26日零晨12:50左右<br />\n離開遊戲後，曾使用Windows 10的ipconfig指令<br />\n先後進行IP release、renew、flushdns<br />\n然後使用tracert指令，<a href=\"http://對facebook.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%B0%8Dfacebook.com&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4SK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=2e7fe3e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">對facebook.com</a>、<a href=\"http://google.com.hk及hkbn.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoogle.com.hk%E5%8F%8Ahkbn.net&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4SK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=09bc30a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">google.com.hk及hkbn.net</a><br />\n進行traceroute，結果再三個測試中<br />\n1 hop為本人之IP gate<br />\n2 hop頭兩次均為 10.239.61.5 第三次為10.239.60.5<br />\n網上查冊，得到 IANA &quot;Private Use&quot; IP addresses<br />\n<br />\n以我所知10.239.xxx.xxx 並非香港IP<br />\n想問連接本地網站時，將條線route到外地係發生咗咩事？<br />\n係唔係有人非法盜取資料？"},{"pid":"e4efaaed17cc6cd424646ec3da7e3624ce13ec64","tid":1943494,"uid":954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T18:22:16.000Z","msg":"google 10.239...<br />\n係hkbn d switch 喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408809958912663ac1cc6ea6d94bbcf4ef60844d","tid":1943494,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4efaaed17cc6cd424646ec3da7e3624ce13ec64","tid":1943494,"uid":954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T18:22:16.000Z","msg":"google 10.239...<br />\n係hkb